Before you begin, make sure you configure .aws/config and .aws/credentials file with aws_access_key_id and aws_secret_access_key
Run aws sts get-caller-identity
git clone https://github.com/xiongye77/terraform-carsales.git
cd terraform-carsales
cd backend
terraform init
terraform apply -auto-approve  # this step will create terraform backend S3 backuet and Dynamodb 
cd ..
cd alb-ecs
terraform init  # the default regin is Sydney ap-southeast-2 which defined in variables.tf file, all ami used for EC2/Bastion host are automatically get 
terraform apply -auto-approve  # this step will create all alb/ec2/ecs/RDS/bastion host/nat gateway/EFS/SSM/Secret manager.... the output will be alb 
